title: Sygic 16.2.4 Cracked
description:
1. Uninstall the previous installation.

2. Delete the Sygic folder from the device.

3. Unzip the downloaded folder on pc.

4. Copy the Sygic folder and apk in your device, during copying pc will ask you to skip some files, don't skip anything, copy everything.

5. Install the application from your device.

6. Don't sign in on first use but you can login or sign up after exiting the first use
